The Encompass Group is working with one of America's premier think tanks in the country and they are looking for a Media Assistant/Associate




The work of their fellows and staff advances ideas rooted in our belief in democracy, free enterprise, American strength and global leadership. As a nonpartisan, nonprofit organization, this non-profit relies on donations from individuals and organizations to support their critical work.




The media relations assistant/associate reports to the director of media relations. Duties include:

Promoting the company's Social, Cultural and Constitutional Studies scholars to media;
